"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"* Crypto = strings of numbers + a collection of mathematical rules for value transfer and computer code triggering\\n  * it’s not tangible\\n  * but it could be highly trustable\\n* Value drives the fundamentals of tokenomics\\n  * What behinds the token to ensure its value?\\n  * What’s the token’s lifecycle? Creation? Management? Removal?\\n  * What’s the incentive structure underlying the tokenomic model? \\n  * How does the structure dictate behaviors that are required in the blockchain system (e.g., safeguarding, transaction validation)? Does incentive theory equal to human behavioral theory? \\n* Tokenomics → financing token incentives + a buff of overall market capitalization \\n  * On different layers:\\n    * Layer 1 Tokens → native for a certain blockchain + powering services on-chain\\n    * Layer 2 Tokens → tokens for Dapps in a certain blockchain\\n  * With different functionalities:\\n    * Security Tokens → investment contracts, passing the Howey Test to earn security credential\\n    * Utility Tokens → financing a network, being issued through ICO\\n  * Fungibility?\\n    * Fungible tokens: the value of tokens is the same, one token could be replaced with each other since containing the exact same value\\n    * Non-fungible tokens (NFT): uniqueness differentiates the value, tokenization of assets, the digital ownership revolution\\n* Common use of Tokens in Tokenomics\\n  * Token distribution\\n    * Rewarding developers, miners who mint new crypto coins\\n    * Token sale\\n    * etc.\\n  * Price stability\\n    * Ensuring an adequate repository of coins in order to matching the level of supply → creating equilibrium\\n    * Supporting an increase in token prices \\n  * Business Scope\\n    * Decentralized marketplaces\\n    * Token leverage \\n    * Ensuring profit distribution by means of financial advantages\\n    * Circulation of token ensures the availability of a robust network\\n  * Governance\\n    * Creating rules → voting, decision-making → ensuring the tokens works as the way it is designed\\n    * Token minting, injection & removal\\n    * #Looking into the details of the project\\n  * Future Readiness\\n    * Growth and maturity of the blockchain network → the need for modification \",\"timestamp\":1640764055,\"title\":\"Tokenomics 101  \"},\"digest\":\"It1K6TbmRpWYETnBC7druUoFba8CkDBh5chaxdoptW0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x73a62aA7fF7842BAA0b97341E0798e29e7f43edc\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"euOpwbJLljcwILObBYFCLUDxXorESGT9lKeCQZ_0xEE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FBJcPtaI7CT2b6dJqYt8NERphWhTCjtzTKa8Vx1aScQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"2LIqQcU6RduRc4ZOvvspxNyWCVWpkKiIkjNvbSMzuDreLpbCwQi0wajFqX5cmEOI-g7Lh0mrNpI2Y7TEnoL2Lw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0b5a68832292a71f392d4144520f2629afc957ff9eeb7860eb59ab644e1aba22660f36ee59c015f968ff6d0f065da120456d80755286d7eef624eb7cdb8576641c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"euOpwbJLljcwILObBYFCLUDxXorESGT9lKeCQZ_0xEE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FBJcPtaI7CT2b6dJqYt8NERphWhTCjtzTKa8Vx1aScQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"It1K6TbmRpWYETnBC7druUoFba8CkDBh5chaxdoptW0\"}"